WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:01.623
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.623 --> 00:00:03.960
I'm excited to be with you all today.

00:00:04.580 --> 00:00:06.160
I really truly am.

00:00:06.160 --> 00:00:08.791
We want to start a new channel.

00:00:08.791 --> 00:00:27.119
I feel in my heart—I have a lot of people that have wanted to sponsor and do things with this channel, but the Lord told me never allow people who were trying to sell a product to be on this channel.

00:00:27.119 --> 00:00:36.114
Now, I thought about putting anointing oils and things like that because you asked for it—anything that has to do with the church, but nothing like t-shirts and things like that.

00:00:36.114 --> 00:00:37.573
Does that make sense?

00:00:37.573 --> 00:00:53.583
I've dedicated this channel to the Father so that He has an avenue to speak to His people, whether He wants to speak through me or if He gives me a word through somebody else—like those last two words that lined up with what He gave me prophetically already.

00:00:54.288 --> 00:00:59.179
So, we've been praying, and my wife is really good at doing eBay.

00:00:59.629 --> 00:01:02.180
We're starting a channel and just announcing it now.

00:01:02.180 --> 00:01:03.800
If you want to follow it, fine.

00:01:03.800 --> 00:01:04.840
If you don't, fine.

00:01:04.840 --> 00:01:06.480
But we're going to be doing a channel.

00:01:06.480 --> 00:01:13.680
It's a blog channel, an everyday channel, as much as my wife is able to because she homeschools the kids and stuff.

00:01:13.680 --> 00:01:20.533
It's a lot of work homeschooling and doing all the things we do because we have a teenager, Braden.

00:01:20.533 --> 00:01:23.947
The channel's name is Come Thrift with Me.

00:01:25.333 --> 00:01:31.416
Our goal for 2024 is teaching people how to do a side hustle.

00:01:32.090 --> 00:01:35.863
There's a lot of people I see who are struggling financially.

00:01:36.125 --> 00:01:42.820
I'm not saying I have it all together, y'all, but I trust God and I believe for everything I have.

00:01:42.820 --> 00:01:46.970
And He has provided a lot through Poshmark and through eBay.

00:01:47.320 --> 00:01:53.520
He gives me places; He'll tell me where to go find the merchandise, the t-shirts, the shoes, or whatever.

00:01:53.520 --> 00:01:54.987
I pray in the car.

00:01:54.987 --> 00:01:58.960
I ask God, 'Show me where do we go today, Father,' and I'm going to do that.

00:01:58.960 --> 00:01:59.872
I'm going to film it.

00:02:00.040 --> 00:02:10.034
I want to show you all how I use the prophetic gifting that God's given me—seeing and knowing—and how I use it to apply to everyday life.

00:02:11.440 --> 00:02:20.183
People think it's always hyper-spiritual, but I'm just a real person who has real needs and needs bills met every single day.

00:02:20.183 --> 00:02:31.626
Just like everyone, once a month, you pay your electric, water, gas, your mortgage, and your car payment; you've got to pay for that stuff unless you're debt-free, which some people are, but most of us aren't.

00:02:33.160 --> 00:02:35.200
And so, we have to believe for food.

00:02:35.200 --> 00:02:36.640
We have to believe for things.

00:02:36.640 --> 00:02:40.651
So, I'm going to show you all that side if you want to watch it.

00:02:41.154 --> 00:02:45.440
Some people might not care; they just want to hear the prophetic words and move on.

00:02:45.440 --> 00:03:02.160
But some people want to hear how to list on eBay, how my wife does inventory, and creative ideas to get extra wealth—doing things like thrifting, showing you what to buy, what not to buy, and what will sell for extra money.

00:03:04.274 --> 00:03:08.034
If you're interested in that and you want to come to our new channel, cool.

00:03:08.697 --> 00:03:18.355
The other part of it was the Lord put it on my heart to show you—I thought about making it fun—doing things I like, as I'm a gun enthusiast.

00:03:18.355 --> 00:03:33.248
I like guns and shooting and being out on the ranch with my dad and showing the Longhorn cattle and riding on the gator, going fishing, popping fireworks, or whatever.

00:03:34.062 --> 00:03:40.640
We have a place where we pop fireworks and camp, doing survival stuff.

00:03:40.640 --> 00:03:56.280
I'll show you what to do with your relatives that are left behind, leaving things for them, and showing you silver coins to barter with—which I feel in my spirit.

00:03:56.280 --> 00:04:01.860
Now, some of you may want to argue about it, and that's fine, but I'm telling you, I believe we're going to see some things ahead.

00:04:02.150 --> 00:04:10.680
I believe with all my heart you need bartering things: bartering food, silver, or maybe some gold little Krugerrands.

00:04:15.529 --> 00:04:16.680
I just have ideas the Lord has given me for a blog.

00:04:17.360 --> 00:04:20.693
I also wanted to update you on my weight loss.

00:04:30.457 --> 00:04:31.547
I've been praying.

00:04:31.547 --> 00:04:40.689
There were so many different ideas about what we should be eating: the carnivore diet, the keto diet, Mediterranean keto, all these different things.

00:04:41.950 --> 00:04:47.776
The first part of January, detoxing from all the sugar I used to consume was brutal.

00:04:48.560 --> 00:04:57.940
I thought I wasn't going to make it through this, but the Lord kept saying, 'You don't have a choice.

00:05:01.973 --> 00:05:03.840
You've got to do this.

00:05:03.840 --> 00:05:08.651
' So I went into prayer and fasting, started doing intermittent fasting, and started interceding.

00:05:08.983 --> 00:05:13.253
One day, the Lord spoke to me—I think it was around January 10th.

00:05:13.538 --> 00:05:18.640
He said to me, because I said, 'Lord, I'm doing carnivore and I'm not losing anything.

00:05:18.640 --> 00:05:19.900
What's going on?

00:05:19.900 --> 00:05:28.160
' I was eating a ton of meat all day long—steak, chicken—I would eat huge plates of meat.

00:05:30.640 --> 00:05:36.359
And the Lord spoke to me and said, 'Brandon, it's about calories.

00:05:36.359 --> 00:05:38.640
You're eating way too much.

00:05:38.640 --> 00:05:46.651
' He said, 'Your body, even if you're on the carnivore diet, cannot burn off all the food that you're consuming.

00:05:46.651 --> 00:05:54.800
So, you need to go back to monitoring how many calories you are consuming on a day-to-day basis.

00:05:54.800 --> 00:06:04.933
' I started adding up how much steak, chicken, turkey, and meat I was eating, and I realized I was eating a ton of calories.

00:06:04.933 --> 00:06:09.140
That's why I wasn't losing weight; my body couldn't burn it all off.

00:06:09.820 --> 00:06:18.160
When it's as cold as it has been, I haven't been able to exercise outside, so of course you're not going to lose weight when consuming so much food.

00:06:18.505 --> 00:06:25.627
The Lord said, 'I want you to monitor every single day how many calories you are consuming.

00:06:25.627 --> 00:06:34.684
' So, I started keeping underneath 1,800 calories.

00:06:36.140 --> 00:06:40.669
My wife, my little researcher, found an app that is phenomenal.

00:06:47.646 --> 00:06:51.246
It monitors your calories and tells you what you're eating.

00:06:51.246 --> 00:07:00.839
You can type in the restaurant, and it shows you exactly what's in it, along with your exercise and how many glasses of water you need every day.

00:07:01.099 --> 00:07:03.786
I think it was about 20 dollars apiece.

00:07:11.379 --> 00:07:14.800
She's doing it with me to help motivate me and we're doing it together.

00:07:14.800 --> 00:07:23.850
She doesn't need to lose any weight, but she's such a blessing helping me log all the drinks and everything I do in a day.

00:07:24.080 --> 00:07:28.810
Keeping on track, I've lost 14 pounds in the last three weeks.

00:07:38.008 --> 00:07:42.453
To God be the glory; I'm going in the right direction.

00:07:42.880 --> 00:07:46.639
It's not always been easy, but I'm drinking my diet shake and logging it.

00:07:54.222 --> 00:08:10.560
Instead of what I used to have for a snack, I'm just trying to find ways to make this a journey that's going to last forever, instead of something like a fad diet that I get burned out on as I have in the past.

00:08:10.560 --> 00:08:13.680
You lose a lot of weight and then you gain it all back.

00:08:13.680 --> 00:08:18.593
I said, 'God, show me how to make this a lifestyle.

00:08:18.593 --> 00:08:19.736
Help me.

00:08:19.736 --> 00:08:32.200
' I know a lot of people struggle with lifestyle changes that lead to yo-yo dieting, where you lose 100 pounds like I'm after and then gain it all back.

00:08:34.800 --> 00:08:39.659
My goal is to have all of my weight off before October.

00:08:39.659 --> 00:08:47.653
The app even shows you that if you maintain these calories every single day, seven days a week, you will be at that weight by October.

00:08:49.440 --> 00:08:51.270
So, I thought it was really cool.

00:08:51.270 --> 00:08:52.608
So, I'm like, let's try it.

00:08:52.896 --> 00:08:55.422
I'm down 14 pounds.

00:08:55.422 --> 00:09:00.112
So, I just wanted to update y'all on the weight loss and where I'm at with it.

00:09:00.112 --> 00:09:01.040
I told you I would.

00:09:01.040 --> 00:09:05.349
I didn't want to make it boring by coming out and telling you every single week.

00:09:06.034 --> 00:09:10.034
But maybe I'll put that on the blog channel—the other channel I told y'all about.

00:09:10.034 --> 00:09:19.268
The channels that we're starting, "Come Thrift With Me," will be about prepping, thrifting, guns, and the fun things.

00:09:19.268 --> 00:09:23.520
Like I said, most people don't agree with carrying guns.

00:09:23.520 --> 00:09:26.114
