00:10:15.559 --> 00:10:15.839
We live in the South, and I was raised with guns my whole life.

00:10:15.839 --> 00:10:19.546
My dad—this is the way our hunters were.

00:10:19.546 --> 00:10:20.990
We're fishers.

00:10:20.990 --> 00:10:22.280
We hunt.

00:10:22.280 --> 00:10:23.570
We fish.

00:10:23.570 --> 00:10:25.138
We do it all.

00:10:25.138 --> 00:10:27.640
That's just the way we are.

00:10:27.640 --> 00:10:33.408
And so most people don't like that, but you'll get over it.

00:10:33.408 --> 00:10:37.028
I mean, that's just the way it is.

00:10:38.338 --> 00:10:40.994
You know, we believe we have a right to defend ourselves and protect our families.

00:10:48.159 --> 00:10:48.479
And so, I'll show you about guns and things like that in another channel and about thrifting.

00:10:48.479 --> 00:10:51.377
It'll be a fun variety of stuff to watch.

00:10:52.011 --> 00:10:55.680
