Lord, we thank you that you come quickly for us.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
You come quickly, Lord.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
We want to go home to be with you in the rapture of the church.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
Jesus, come quickly.

